LevelBuilder.jar is a swing based GUI which allows for the creation of tile based levels to be
made easily and quickly.

Note:
-Greater than ~25 tiles onscreen causes some screen flickering

################################################################################################
##     Can't launch from inside AndroidStudio                                                 ##
##     Launch LevelBuilder from file explorer (right click > show in explorer)                ##
################################################################################################

(If you do attempt to launch from Android studio and can't run the main app,
change the run dialog beside the run icon from LevelBuilder.jar to app)

The code is on the svn under Lunar Game Tools as an eclipse project if you want to have a look.
A zip file of project is also included.

If you have any ideas, questions, bugs, let me know.